name: MultipleBreasts
description:
Finally a Multiple Breast Lora (that is if I had actually uploaded this a few days ago like I had intended. Go check out ChineseRoom's model as well).

This model is designed to give a character 4 breasts to furry/anthro characters rather than just 2, though might be able to preserve any extra breasts in img2img.

This model works best when using either V2 or V1 in parallel with V1.5 at a weight of 0.5-0.75 each. Also don't let the samples fool you, it isn't designed just for dragons and V2 isn't even trained on any, I just like dragons.

modelVersions.name: V2
modelVersions.description:
V2 is trained on a few hand-picked images and offers decent breasts without affecting the art style too much. Sadly that also means pose variation isn't the best, but isn't too bad either.

Best used at or around a weight of 1. Can also be used in parallel with V1 or V1.5 at a lower weight for better results.
